ZH: 我收到了一条好消息。
EN: I received good news.

ZH: 他非常关心你的消息。
EN: He cares a lot about your news.

ZH: 我需要你迅速告诉我最新消息。
EN: I need you to quickly inform me of the latest news.

ZH: 昨天晚上我接到了一个未知的消息。
EN: I received an unknown message last night.

ZH: 他们在消息中提到了你的名字。
EN: They mentioned your name in the message.

ZH: 我们需要追踪并确认这个消息的真实性。
EN: We need to track and verify the authenticity of this news.

ZH: 她在新闻中得知了这个消息。
EN: She learned about this news from the media.

ZH: 请保密这个消息，不要告诉任何人。
EN: Please keep this news confidential and don't tell anyone.

ZH: 这个消息对他来说是个巨大的打击。
EN: This news is a huge blow to him.

ZH: 警方尚未发布任何关于事件的消息。
EN: The police have not released any information about the incident yet.

ZH: 我经常通过电视新闻了解世界各地的消息。
EN: I often learn about news from around the world through television.

ZH: 如果你有任何问题，请随时询问，我会及时回复你的消息。
EN: If you have any questions, please feel free to ask, and I will respond to your message promptly.

ZH: 看到这个消息后，我感到非常吃惊。
EN: I was very surprised when I saw this news.

ZH: 我们不能仅仅依赖社交媒体上的消息，我们还需要进行进一步的调查。
EN: We can't rely solely on the news from social media; we need to conduct further investigation.

ZH: 这个消息影响了人们对市场的信心。
EN: This news has affected people's confidence in the market.

ZH: 他的微信上充斥着废话和无关紧要的消息。
EN: His WeChat is filled with nonsense and irrelevant messages.

ZH: 经纪人向他发送了一条新消息，询问他是否有兴趣接受新的项目。
EN: His agent sent him a new message, asking if he is interested in taking on a new project.

ZH: 我很长时间没有和他通话了，但我经常通过短信交流消息。
EN: I haven't spoken to him for a long time, but we often exchange messages through text.

ZH: 这个软件可以实时发送最新的新闻消息。
EN: This app can send real-time news updates.

ZH: 你知道最近有什么有趣的消息吗？
EN: Do you know any interesting news recently?
